==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: ĕr shú néng xiáng
===Etymology===
Literally: so familiar to the ears, that it can be (told) in detail
===Idiom===
'''[[耳]][[熟]][[能]][[详]]'''
# heard a million times, to the point where one can recite it in one's sleep; well-worn (phrase)
#: ''[[以下]][[就]][[让]][[我们]][[来]][[看]][[一些]]'''耳熟能详'''[[的]][[中文]][[在]][[英语]][[中]][[是]][[如何]][[表达]][[的]]''
#: ''Below, let us take a look at how some '''well-worn''' Chinese phrases are expressed in English''
